Package it.polimi.ingsw.client.gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChoicePopup
    ChoicePopup is a subclass of Stage, composed by an AnchorPane, which allows the user to do a choice through a choiceBox in the setup phase
    EndGameMessage
    Game over message created in the end of the match to show if the player has lost or won
    GodCardsPopup
    This class is a Stage which shows the cards contained in godCardsDescriptions keyValues(), used for setup purpose, to choose match/player cards, and during the match to show matchGodCards powers.
    Gui  
    GuiButton
    Generic button which extends Button class and can be created with more specific parameters
    GuiClient
    JavaFX App
    GuiMap
    Subclass of the abstract class GameMap
    HomeScene
    The home scene is composed by an AnchorPane with two nameTags composed by a StackPane with an image and a TextField to insert IP and Port values, and a play button which sends a request of connection.
    PlayerSetupPopup
    Subclass of Stage with two Text and TextField objects for the insertion of nickname and date and a submit button
